{"tid":1866581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當有一日中國起義 你會唔會支持佢地 甚至幫佢地?","createTime":"2020-02-06T19:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T20:54:27.000Z","uid":266672,"like":17,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c7234c770487ad3feb764c7e7b3b155b7210ae0f","tid":1866581,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T19:56:50.000Z","msg":"假設有一日有記者係中國街頭既訪問下<br />\n<br />\n每一個都係話 抱歉 我們以前放棄了自由 但現在我們想把自由拿回來<br />\n<br />\n每一個都係話 抱歉 我們以前不懂也不支持香港 但我現在希望香港能為我們打氣<br />\n<br />\n佢地會唔會打動到你地?<br />\n<br />\n當有一日 我地要同中國既同胞一齊打共產黨 你又會唔會?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />會 係依一刻打贏左大佬先算 之後既事之後先算<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔係 做狗都唔做支那人 點都唔會支持佢地 佢死佢地事<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又或者其實係我FF得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3524702708d9aefb44d57b67379f58cc90591d82","tid":1866581,"uid":237425,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:09:53.000Z","msg":"香港守住邊境同所有岸邊就可以，食花生<br />\n<br />\n全民皆兵守住村口街口<br />\n運兵車載滿港軍隨時支援一切可能發生戰鬥既地區"},{"pid":"598277bdecf53d06bf21869fa43bbe1e5eef9221","tid":1866581,"uid":28921,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:14:46.000Z","msg":"大陸佬反轉豬肚就係屎<br />\n你幫完佢分分鐘俾人食埋<br />\n<br />\n食下花生算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144928f9bc3ea7a4131094525b9cd356e8b28636","tid":1866581,"uid":146030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:15:41.000Z","msg":"要用深圳同萬山群島換我哋支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c659fc7f01e3f2bbf168a459aa9ec55e35d2adec","tid":1866581,"uid":263261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T20:16:47.000Z","msg":"有行動既支持冇問題<br />\n做冷氣軍